rean relations updated the new york times let them eat rockets search fsi search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages news of interest siegfried hecker testifies before congress on governance of nuclear security march 14 2012 cisac in the news siegfried hecker what i found in north korea cisac in the news physics today on february 23 2011 hecker interviewed on npr about documents related to north korea's plutonium program cisac in the news national public radio on may 13 2008 cisac's hecker analyzes challenges to denuclearizing north korea april 24 2008 cisac news siegfried hecker's report on north korea visit to senate foreign relations committee march 25 2008 cisac fsi stanford news cisac's hecker speaks on pbs newshour about north korea nuclear test cisac in the news pbs newshour on october 9 2006 support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 723 4581 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
